Basics
------

First, read "verbs" for a basic discourse on the difference between
verbs and commands.

Basic commands:

end	Retire your character
help	See help
mail	Check your mail/send a new message
play	Start playing a character
quit	Stop playing and return to reality
tell	Send a private message

Basic verbs:

go	Move through an exit
look	View an object or the room you're in
say	Say something

See also:
	channels, death, verbs
